### Create a new decision
POST http://localhost:9000/decisions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Choose a Programming Language",
  "criteria": [
    {
      "decisionId": 0,
      "name": "Learning Curve",
      "weight": 8
    },
    {
      "decisionId": 0,
      "name": "Performance",
      "weight": 7
    },
    {
      "decisionId": 0,
      "name": "Community Support",
      "weight": 9
    }
  ],
  "options": [
    {
      "decisionId": 0,
      "name": "Kotlin"
    },
    {
      "decisionId": 0,
      "name": "Python"
    },
    {
      "decisionId": 0,
      "name": "JavaScript"
    }
  ]
}

### Get a decision by ID (replace {id} with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:9000/decisions/1
Accept: application/json

### Health check endpoint
GET http://localhost:9000/ping

